abstract: Democrats in California are accusing the state’s Republicans of trying to sabotage the new state-run health insurance exchange by putting up their own website that Democrats call misleading. Republicans say they’re just trying to help consumers confused by the new law.

headline.main: Parties in California Squabble Over Another Website
